(13, 1, '2016-05-15 11:14:02', '2016-05-15 11:14:02', 'The Barrier Reef Orchestra was formed in Townsville in 2000 after a workshop conducted by Richard McIntyre from Canberra. We are a community orchestra, drawing players from a large cross section of the Townsville community and sometimes beyond. All are drawn together by their great love of orchestral music and desire to provide North Queensland with quality performances.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #3366ff;">Become a part of the Barrier Reef Orchestra Today!</span></h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe are always looking for more people to join our wonderful community, if you''re interested in being a member or becoming apart of the music you join by going to <a href="http://localhost/wordpress/join/" target="_blank">Join Us Page</a>, of if you''re interested in contributing to our community you can on the <a href="http://localhost/wordpress/contribute/">Contribute page</a>!\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #3366ff;">Check out our latest events!</span></h3>\r\nKeep up to date with the Orchestra by checking out our <a href="http://localhost/wordpress/events/">Events page</a>!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<a href="http://localhost/wordpress/join" ><h1 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #ff6600;">SIGN UP WITH US TODAY!!!!</span></h1></a>\r\n<img class="size-full wp-image-98 aligncenter" src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/background_bro_08.jpg" alt="background_bro_08" width="980" height="265" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home', '', '', '2016-05-19 12:38:03', '2016-05-19 12:38:03', '', 0, 'http://127.0.0.1/wordpress/?page_id=13', 0, 'page', '', 0),
