(119, 1, '2016-05-17 12:21:26', '2016-05-17 12:21:26', 'The Barrier Reef Orchestra was formed in Townsville in 2000 after a workshop conducted by Richard McIntyre from Canberra. We are a community orchestra, drawing players from a large cross section of the Townsville community and sometimes beyond. All are drawn together by their great love of orchestral music and desire to provide North Queensland with quality performances.\r\n\r\nWe are always looking for more people to join our wonderful community, if you''re interested in being a member or becoming apart of the music you join by going to <a href="http://wordpress/join/" target="_blank">Join Us Page</a>, of if you''re interested in contributing to our community you can on the <a href="http://wordpress/contribute/">Contribute page</a>!', 'Welcome to the Barrier Reef Orchestra!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'welcome-to-the-barrier-reef-orchestra', '', '', '2016-05-17 12:21:26', '2016-05-17 12:21:26', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=119', 0, 'post', '', 0),
